      "span_text": "We assume the scintillator is a Saint-Gobain BC-408 plastic scintillator and the PMTs are Hamamatsu R329-02 PMTs, as in Ref. in performing calculations of these quantities, but specific scintillator and PMT choices can be later optimized for actual installation in this context."
